  "title": "Kitchen Crew / Service Crew / 5day (Japanese Restaurant)",
  "description": "<p>Established Japanese Cuisine Brand Looking for:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>1) </strong><u><strong>Kitchen Crew</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare, cook, and assemble food items according to daily operational needs and company standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure high standards of hygiene and cleanliness in all kitchen areas.</li>\n  <li>Assist in dishwashing duties when required.</li>\n  <li>Perform other duties assigned by the kitchen manager or supervisors.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2. </strong><u><strong>Service Crew</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Welcome and greet customers warmly to ensure a positive dining experience.</li>\n  <li>Take customer orders accurately and serve food and beverages promptly.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and organisation of the service and dining areas.</li>\n  <li>Carry out other duties as assigned by the manager or supervisors.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Basic $1750, Joining Bonus $1000</p>\n<p>Besides, we offer an attractive package of benefits, including:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>AWS (Annual Wage Supplement)</strong> &amp; performance-based bonus</li>\n  <li><strong>Annual leave + public holiday entitlement</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Birthday vouchers</strong> to celebrate your special day</li>\n  <li><strong>Medical &amp; dental insurance</strong> for your well-being</li>\n  <li><strong>Complimentary staff meals</strong> during shifts</li>\n  <li><strong>Overtime pay entitlement</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Career progression opportunities</strong> within the company</li>\n  <li><strong>Uniform provided</strong> &amp; <strong>full training</strong> to set you up for success</li>\n</ul>\n<p>5 days per week, 44 hours in total (hours subject to outlet schedule), with at least 30 hours of overtime monthly.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>** No experience? No problem – we provide full on-the-job training.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
